newsitem.title: EU: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ C 316 OF OCTOBER 25, 1996.
newsitem.headline: OFFICIAL JOURNAL CONTENTS - OJ C 316 OF OCTOBER 25, 1996.

text.p: (Note - contents are displayed in reverse order to that in the printed Journal)

Phare - reconstruction of 'Olszyna' motorway junction Within the framework of the European Commission Phare Cross-Border Cooperation Programme Poland-Germany Regional Board of Public Roads in Zielona Gora invites contractors who meet the conditions and have sufficient experience and references to participate in the international, open tendering procedure (96/C 316/10)
Proposal for a Council Regulation amending Regulation (EEC) No 3760/92 establishing a Community system for fisheries and aquaculture (96/C 316/08) COM(96) 350 final - 96/0183(CNS)

Proposal for a Council Regulation on the implementation by the Commission of activities to promote market access for Community industry to third countries (96/C 316/07) COM(96) 432 final - 96/0219(ACC)
Non-opposition to a notified concentration (Case No IV/M.806 - British Airways/TAT (II)) (96/C 316/06)
Notice pursuant to Article 19 (3) of Council Regulation No 17 concerning notification No IV/34.774 - Potacan (96/C 316/05)

Summary of Community decisions on marketing authorizations in respect of medicinal products from 15 September 1996 to 15 October 1996 (Published pursuant to Article 12 or Article 34 of Council Regulation (EEC) No 2309/93 (1)) (96/C 316/04)
Commission communication as part of the implementation of Directive 89/106/EEC on construction products (1) as amended by Council Directive 93/68/EEC (2) (96/C 316/03)
COUNCIL DECISION of 15 October 1996 renewing the Management Board of the European Centre for the Development of Vocational Training (96/C 316/01) END OF DOCUMENT.
